Hi, <%= @user.first_name %>
===============================================
This is your weekly WePray praylist digest:

Subscribed Requests:
     <% @user.subscribed_requests.each do |request| %>
     <%= subscription.request.firstname ? subscription.request.user.first_name : subscription.request.user.username %> 
	 <%= request.content %>
     <%= subscription.request.content %>
	 <%= subscription.request.request %>
      <% end %>

Prayed Requests:
      <% if @user.email_prays == true 
          @user.prayers.each do |prayer|
            if prayer.updated_at > Time.now - 1.week %>
     	<%= prayer.request.firstname ? prayer.request.user.first_name : prayer.request.user.username %>
     	<%= prayer.request.content %>
        <%  end 
          end 
        end %>
 
Thanks for praying for your church family!


